---
title: Speedy Indian Turkey Wraps Warmed Tortillas and Garlic Sauce
description: In a hurry? These Indian-inspired tacos will be on the table in 20!  Indian-spiced veggies and succulent turkey get wrapped in warmed tortillas with a tasty garlic sauce. Wrap it up and hit the road.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/speedy-indian-turkey-wraps-e81f4780.jpg
